	<!-- Rules / Options Attributes 
	     * rounds: Versus = 0,1,2=>1,3,5 rounds; non-Versus = first to 0-2=>1-3 wins
	     * AI difficulty: 0=Easy, 1=Med, 2=Hard 
	     * round length: value => value+1 minutes
	     * reset arenas: 0=no, 1=yes
	-->
